105
00:09:13,858 --> 00:09:14,899
I'm just saying.

106
00:09:15,739 --> 00:09:26,489
You know, of course, as the mayor mentioned, the police department are our closest partners and we are happy to see them have this new facility to do their work.

107
00:09:26,869 --> 00:09:33,855
But I want to spend a minute just talking about what the groundbreaking for this new building means for the citizens of Medford.

108
00:09:35,577 --> 00:09:39,040
Think about what we ask of our police departments today.

109
00:09:40,149 --> 00:09:57,807
We ask them to do impeccable investigations, to use technology that literally changes every day, to ensure that we preserve evidence in a way that leads to convictions that are unassailable.

110
00:09:58,948 --> 00:10:03,012
We ask them to be here when you are lost,

111
00:10:03,980 --> 00:10:10,785
when you need help, when your family hurts, that's what we ask of our police departments.

112
00:10:11,586 --> 00:10:21,333
And there is probably no discipline that in the last 15 years has changed more and has risen to that challenge.

113
00:10:22,193 --> 00:10:30,960
No matter what people say, no matter what their take is on the issue, when they are hurt, they need help.

114
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:32,281
They dial 911.

115
00:10:34,002 --> 00:10:44,729
And to have people here that we treat with dignity and show that by the places we give them to work is a very, very important statement by a community.

116
00:10:45,510 --> 00:10:54,316
You can be certain in Medford that you have chosen well in the people who lead you, in the people who guide your public safety.

117
00:10:55,502 --> 00:11:01,844
As the New Testament tells us, where your treasure is, that is where your heart is.

118
00:11:02,764 --> 00:11:13,468
And by making the stand to commit funds to this building, Medford has truly shown the community where the heart and the soul of this city lay.

119
00:11:13,908 --> 00:11:14,568
So thank you.

120
00:11:14,609 --> 00:11:18,230
I'm great looking forward to this building and I'm happy to be here this morning.

121
00:11:18,310 --> 00:11:18,710
Thank you.

